Title: [ANN] [ICO] [AIRDROP] MUXE - innovative platform for all real estate needs
Body: 1. Useof Funds  *Development 40%    Funds will be used to constantly upgrade technology and improve the platform experience for our users. Funds will also be used to fuel the daily  operational expenses like hosting fees, transaction fees, overheads, and equipment.   *OverseasOperations 20%   To set up teams in USA, Europe and Asia to market and promote the platform. The teams will be responsible for tie ups with their local companies to  participate with MUXE.  *Marketing 20%   This marketing budget will be used to acquire customers and business partners to join our platform and ecosystem. This icludes use of digital ads, online  and offline promotions, road shows, trade shows and referral campaigns to drive adoption and spread awareness.  *Partnership 10%   MUXE will need funds to facilitate and structure deals with potential business partners in the industry. This includes swaps, sponsorships, purchases,  expenses and other miscellaneous costs needed to form these important partnerships.  *Security & Legal 10%   We will be conducting audits and checks on our platform regularly with our business partners and users. To ensure that we are operating legally in all  jurisdiction globally.  2. Partnerships   Partners and Consultants recognize the potential of MUXE becoming one of the best blockchain companies in the crypto industry. Since the initiation of  this project.    MUXE has garnered many partners from tech companies to contractors namely VOISE, BitcoinToken, BlockXperience, Twinto, NewTech, Flexchainand  many more.  3. The value of MUXE token will increase because of its Core Values (P.8.) , Vision (P.7) , and Objectives (P.9) .  4. How It Works   The MUXE platform allows their users to list for rent, buy or sell of properties, contract services, scheduling movers, to purchasing home improvement  equipment.     MUXE token is the cryptocurrency for all transactions on the platform. Our blockchain technology is based on Ethereum ERC20 platform.  I hope it will help you

Title: [ANN] [ICO] [AIRDROP] MUXE - innovative platform for all real estate needs
Body: MUXE token is the cryptocurrency for all transactions on the platform that will be used for purchases of home, office supplies, rental payments to contractors' fees. MUXE platform provides a wide range of varied products and services to cater to almost everyone's need from a home supplies or office renovation to property development projects. It is a single decentralized platform using Blockchain technology and cryptocurrency for transactions. This revolutionary platform will provide the convenience, increase efficiency and money (time) saving for their users. The MUXE platform allows users to easily LIST, SEARCH, BUY and SELL real estate related products and services on a secured P2P platform using blockchain technology It is the one-stop real estate products and services platform that can integrate blockchain technology with MUXE tokens for real estate industry. MUXE is easily accessed, convenient, private and secured for everyone to perform their transactions.

Author: MuxeProject
Title: [ANN] [ICO] [AIRDROP] MUXE - innovative platform for all real estate needs
Body: MUXE B.V. is registered in the Netherlands in full compliance to the Dutch law. How it began was with numerous conversations about blockchain technology amongst my co founders and tech friends. Then we recognized the potential and opportunity of cryptocurrency market before concluding that; we want to create a platform that connects the global community with blockchain. After several sessions of brainstorming sessions and consultations with industry experts, it was conclusive that there is no single platform that caters to all the needs of the real estate businesses.  In some form or another we all had our misadventures or interesting experiences with home repairs, renovations or looking for a home or a place to rent. So came the concept of a single solution platform inspired MUXE to create the ultimate one stop Real Estate business platform using tokens. Body: MUXE Forms a Beneficial Partnership with VOISE The MUXE team continuously strives towards success in developments as a business to ensure the highest quality of standards and products are introduced. This includes forming significant relationships with other businesses which is taken very seriously by the MUXE team. With that being said, we have made a strategic and beneficial partnership today. This partnership has been in the works for a few weeks and now we can officially make the announcement.  Our new joining partner is VOISE! We are incredibly excited to introduce VOISE as our partner. VOISE is a token based medium for artists in the music industry to post their music and earn their fair share in proceeds. The recording industry has undercut earnings from artists and songwriters regularly and had been for many decades. VOISE cuts out the middleman and gives as close to 100% of the artists revenue to the artist who created it. MUXE and VOISE have similar goals and an outlook toward helping the undercut community. We both believe that everyone should benefit the most from their hard work and receive their fare earnings. Although we are in different industries, our values align to a point where our partnership would be beneficial. VOISE will be providing MUXE with mentorship and other significant resources MUXE lacks, while MUXE provides resources and expertise in areas VOISE may lack. Our belief in decentralized and value creating properties of our companies will be what makes our partnership beneficial. We are both committed to the betterment of the community and to the crypto market by adding transparency, trust, ethics, and hard work to our companies.  The nature of our partnership is not officially written yet. However, it will be discussed further over the coming weeks. We will keep the community updated on any major developments as they come in. Together we will share our networks and resources and help each other to move forward in the crypto market and change the world for the better.     #VOISE #MUXErealestate #ethereum #ERC20 #collaboration #bitcoin #crypto #hardwork #success #investments #HeartheVOISEofMUXE #partnerships #progress

Body: F.A.Q.  When will MUXE get listed on CoinMarketCap? To get listed on CoinMarketCap MUXE has to have at least $100,000 USD equivalent of daily trading volume on exchanges. Currently the focus is on a number of fundamental steps to create a strong and stable brand for MUXE. When that preparation is complete, adding MUXE on CoinMarketCap is certainly one of the goals. Thank you for joining this adventure with us and we look forward to achieve all our ambitious goals together.  Why does MUXE enter into partnerships? We believe it's good to enter into partnerships with other crypto projects that we believe in as a team. When the MUXE team believes that a new partner has a good vision and expertise in certain areas, such as marketing, it can be interesting to join forces and make use of each other's expertise.  What we are all part of now is that a new digital economy based on Blockchain is expanding and has many other rules than the current fiat economy. This also requires new specific expertise in marketing and the way in which digital projects are organized.  If you have any more questions, please take a look into the MUXE Support Base. If your question is not listed, please don't hesitate and ask it, we are happy to answer the question as soon as possible. Thank you for your interest.

Title: [ANN] [ICO] [AIRDROP] MUXE - innovative platform for all real estate needs
Body: For those that are wondering why our Twitter currently seems to be deactivated, we have a very simple explanation. Please read the GDPR statement below   GDPR Regulations in Europe change the internet The internet and data processing is changing with the new privacy laws that have occurred since the 25th of May.  The EU General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) replaces the Data Protection Directive 95/46/EC and was designed to harmonize data privacy laws across Europe, to protect and empower all EU citizens data privacy and to reshape the way organizations across the region approach data privacy.  The MUXE team is fully aware of these changes and we are adopting them into all our products and services. Meanwhile, unfortunately, because of the GDPR laws we are going through some issues with our Twitter profile. Twitter has therefor deactivated our Twitter account at this moment. We are doing everything we can to work this issue out with Twitter to reactivate our account as soon as possible.
